window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Jeremiah and his new Flannel Army are on a mission to make all of North America part of his growing empire. Along the way, he will face powerful enemies, including a man who rivals Jeremiah in power and dissenters within his own camp. Can Jeremiah escape treachery, turn enemies into allies, and defeat the powerful monsters that stand in his way, all while establishing himself as the true King of the Continent? King of the Continent is the third book book in the Integrated Universe series, an epic fantasy adventure which draws inspiration from a variety of popular role-playing games.</p>"; 
